         <div type="bibliography" subtype="edition">
            <ab>A few words were read in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:bergaigne-1888"/>: <biblScope>192</biblScope></bibl>; some more in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:aymonier-1891"/>: <biblScope>52-53</biblScope></bibl>; partially summarised in English, in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:majumdar-1927"/>: <biblScope>209</biblScope></bibl>, whence <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:golzio-2004"/>: <biblScope>183</biblScope></bibl>. It was studied in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:jacques-1977"/>: <biblScope>1079-1080</biblScope></bibl> but was integrally published for the first time in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:ECIC-IV"/>: <biblScope><seg type="check">forthcoming</seg></biblScope></bibl>, which publication is reproduced here.</ab>
